                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5106" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0748</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9227 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">并溢商誉＿赌减风险＿对赌协议是并购风险防控的九阳真经吗</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot;Combination&quot; overflows goodwill, &quot;gambling&quot; reduces risks, is the gambling agreement the &quot;Nine Suns&quot; of M&amp;A risk prevention and control</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">胡庆十，吴培，陈珂</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安徽师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华谊兄弟传媒股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">文化、体育和娱乐业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">并购风险；商誉减值；对赌协议；华谊兄弟；东阳美拉</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">M&amp;A risk; impairment of goodwill; gambling agreement; Huayi Brothers; Dongyang Meira;</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">对赌协议作为一种风险控制机制，因能够降低并购风险发生的可能性而被广泛运用于企业并购中。本案例聚焦华谊兄弟采用对赌协议并购东阳美拉的过程，发现并购双方针对业绩的承诺和协议的执行，反复博弈，最终陷入对赌“囚徒困境”。华谊兄弟作为曾经影视行业的领头羊，自2009年上市以来市值一路飙升，在2015年达到顶峰，如今距离当年巅峰时刻缩水近700亿元；由此引发思考：企业期望通过并购扩大规模，却事与愿违造成商誉溢价；期望通过设计对赌以降低并购风险，最终因业绩承诺未果造成并购困局，孰是孰非？本案例通过抽丝剥茧，深度展现这个过程，引发对对赌协议与并购风险防控关系的思考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As a risk control mechanism, gambling agreements are widely used in corporate mergers and acquisitions because they can reduce the possibility of merger risks. This case focuses on the process of Huayi Brothers&#39; acquisition of Dongyang Meira using a gambling agreement, and it is found that the two parties involved in the merger have repeatedly played games with respect to the performance commitments and implementation of the agreement, and eventually fell into the gambling &quot;prisoner&#39;s dilemma&quot;. As a leader in the film and television industry, Huayi Brothers has soared its market value since its listing in 2009. It reached its peak in 2015. It has now shrunk by nearly 70 billion yuan from its peak that year. This has led to thinking: companies have expanded their business scale through mergers and acquisitions, but Backfires caused a thunderstorm of goodwill; it was hoped to reduce the risk of mergers and acquisitions through designing a gambling, and eventually the mergers and acquisitions dilemma caused by the unsuccessful performance promises, what is right? This case demonstrates this process in depth by drawing a little bit and peeling off the cocoon, and triggers thinking about the relationship between gambling agreements and M&amp;A risk prevention and control.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务会计理论与实务》、《高级财务管理》、《创业管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业并购、财务风险、风险控制、商誉减值</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
